Table 1. Crystal data and structure refinement for polymers 1 and 2

| Polymers | 1 | 2 |
|----------|---|---|
| Empirical formula | C18H28CoN6O12 | C20H22CoN6O4S2 |
| Formula weight | 579.39 | 533.49 |
| Temperature (K) | 291(2) | 291(2) |
| Wavelength (Å) | 0.71073 | 0.71073 |
| Crystal system | monoclinic | monoclinic |
| Space group | P21/c | P21/c |
| a (Å) | 8.0638(16) | 6.6946(13) |
| b (Å) | 14.039(3) | 13.635(3) |
| c (Å) | 11.281(2) | 12.950(3) |
| α (°) | 90 | 90 |
| β (°) | 91.26(3) | 99.72(3) |
| γ (°) | 90 | 90 |
| Volume (Å³) | 1276.8(4) | 1165.1(4) |
| Z (calculated density) | 2 | 2 |
| Dc (g cm⁻³) | 1.497 | 1.521 |
| Absorption coefficient (mm⁻¹) | 0.740 | 0.955 |
| F(000) | 598 | 550 |
| Crystal sizes (mm) | 0.28×0.20×0.18 | 0.28×0.25×0.20 |
| θ Range for data collection (°) | 2.32–24.99 | 2.19–27.50 |
| Index ranges | 0⩽h⩽9; −16⩽k⩽16; −13⩽l⩽13 | 0⩽h⩽8; −16⩽k⩽16; −16⩽l⩽16 |
| Reflections collected/unique | 3097/1810 | 3458/2003 |
| Observed reflections (I>2σ(I)) | 1574 | 1707 |
| Rint | 0.0482 | 0.0457 |
| Data/restraints/parameters | 1810/0/198 | 2003/0/168 |
| Goodness-of-fit[^a] on F² | 1.084 | 1.132 |
| Final R[^b] indices [I>2σ(I)] | R1=0.0553; wR2=0.1279 | R1=0.0614; wR2=0.1499 |
| R indices (all data) | R1=0.0751; wR2=0.1351 | R1=0.0795; wR2=0.1581 |

[^a]: GOF=∑w(|Fo|−|Fc|)²/(Nobserved−Nparameters)²^(1/2)
[^b]: R=∑∥Fo|−|Fc∥/∑|Fo|, wR=∑w(|Fo|−|Fc|)²/∑wFo²^(1/2), w=1/[σ²(Fo²)+(aP)²+bP](P=[2Fc²+max(Fo²,0)])/3); a=0.0534, b=0.0000 (1); a=0.0781, b=1.1089 (2).
